ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectRegulations Amending the General Preferential Tariff and Least Developed Country Tariff Rules of Origin Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the GENERAL PREFERENTIAL TARIFF AND LEAST DEVELOPED COUNTRY TARIFF RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS in order to implement the Budget 2017 initiative to improve market access for least developed countries by allowing them to use manufacturing inputs sourced from, and processed in, an expanded list of countries in the production of T-shirts and pants that qualify for duty-free importation into Canada.
